data.description: Such a delightful residence that promises a warm and inviting atmosphere from the moment you step inside. This adorable bungalow is perfectly designed for those who appreciate the fusion of cozy comfort with an open and airy layout. The exterior is just as inviting with a quaint front porch that beckons you to enjoy a quiet morning w/a cup of coffee. Large fenced backyard on a corner lot creates an oasis w/a firepit outdoor dining experience superb for spring entertaining w/friends. Highlighted features of this home include tiled bathroom flooring & showers, laminate hardwood floors, stainless steel appliances, large walk in closet in primary bedroom, HVAC & roof replaced in 2017, windows replaced in 2016. More than just a place to live, it's a sanctuary that offers the blend of warmth, character and functionality. Don't miss the opportunity to make this charming house your home.
